<h1>Confirm your TFT Smart Hub account</h1>

<p>Hello <%= @user.display_name.presence || @user.email %>,</p>

<p>Thanks for signing up for TFT Smart Hub! Use the verification code below to confirm your email address:</p>

<p style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 6px; margin: 16px 0;">
  <%= @verification_token %>
</p>

<p>You can also click the button below to open the verification screen with your code prefilled:</p>

<p>
  <a href="<%= @verification_url %>" style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 20px; background-color: #4361ee; color: #ffffff; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none;">
    Verify my email
  </a>
</p>

<p>The code will expire in 2 hours. If you didn’t create an account, you can safely ignore this email.</p>

<p>— The TFT Smart Hub team</p>
